title: Spore Creature Creator: Expanded CSA_Main.package
description:
This file was copied out of the full install of the Creature Creator for Spore and as such, it is only the CSA_Main.package file compressed into a rar.

To be able to unlock the new parts, just extract CSA_Main.rar to (C:\ Program Files\ Electronic Arts\ SPORE\ Data)



Also, despite what many people are saying this does not unlock 75% of the total parts, not by a long shot. It really only unlocks around 50% or so, but still it&#039;s better than nothing.
